<title>SOUTH AFRICA: S.African April gold/forex reserves detailed.</title>
<headline>S.African April gold/forex reserves detailed.</headline>
<dateline>PRETORIA 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The South African Reserve Bank on Thursday released a detailed breakdown of its gold and foreign exchange reserves as at April 30 1997.</p>
<p>The headline figure of 14.4 billion rand was announced on May 2.</p>
<p>(Rand million)	    Apr '97	     Mar '97     Apr '96</p>
<p>Assets:</p>
<p>Gold		    5313.31	     5061.42     7168.18</p>
<p>Foreign		 9102.79	     8058.76     4525.80</p>
<p>Total		  14416.10	    13120.18    11693.97</p>
<p>Gold volume		3.90  million oz	3.64	  4.64</p>
<p>Gold value	    1363.30  rand/oz  1391.01     1543.62</p>
<p>Other liabilities	8.01  bln rand    8.08	  6.21</p>
<p>Total liabilities     35.77  bln rand   36.18	 33.21</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom (+27 11 482-1003)</p>
